claim.claim-text:
9. A system comprising:
a database to store identity resources of a user;
a server coupled to the database and configured to:
receive information from a user of an open overlay service that binds a plurality of associated identity resources of the user to a unique identifier of the user;
receive a request to contact the user from another user of the open overlay service based on a selected one of the plurality of associated identity resources of the user known by the another user; and
restrict views of the another user for the identity of the user to the selected one of the plurality of associated identity resources.
